{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 1028217, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 204076, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "不实施军队国家化，军队中立化，就永远不可能有民主", "timestamp": 1612141077, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1028308, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 204076, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "wg你说是d指挥枪还是枪指挥d？", "timestamp": 1612143322, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1028309, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 204076, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "从来就没什么中立化，从来都是枪杆子里出政权", "timestamp": 1612143345, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1028310, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 204076, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 苏联信了这套，然后呢？", "timestamp": 1612143364, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1028381, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 204076, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 可美国英国法国一直都是这套，也没见出问题", "timestamp": 1612144538, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1028384, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 204076, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 在成熟的民主国家，军队国家化是一种必然，但是在民主转型过程中，军队和国家分立很容易导致政变。智利，埃及等国民主的中断都是由于军队中立未被贯彻", "timestamp": 1612144620, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1028408, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 204076, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 暴力是夺权的手段，但是暴力不能带来正当性，正当的权威有三种形式，传统型，卡里斯玛型，法理型。如果承认宪法最高，依照宪法选举产生的领导人就有最高的合法性，法理型权威就被构建了。此时，非中立的军队的作用就更多地体现为随时可能摧毁宪法秩序而非维护宪法秩序。", "timestamp": 1612145020, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1028415, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 204076, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "我论证得比较简陋，总之就是，要实行西方民主，就要军队国家化。如果不打算实施西方民主，自然也不是很需要军队国家化。既实施西方民主，有军队不中立，这就是畸形政体，随时可能崩溃。", "timestamp": 1612145169, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1028583, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 204076, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 窝小想复读经济决定论", "timestamp": 1612147222, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1029936, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 204076, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 正确", "timestamp": 1612165668, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 5, "pid": 204076, "reply": 10, "tag": "政治相关", "text": "# 快讯 新华社快讯：缅甸全国民主联盟发言人1日说，缅甸国务资政昂山素季、总统温敏及一些民盟高级官员被军方扣押。 ​", "timestamp": 1612138432, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1612165667, "url": "", "vote": {}}}